{"tid":1627252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到14歲中槍少年睇到】冇理由原告變被告  一定要告黑警同政府","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:17:13.000Z","uid":262428,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2686db6a7f48051b5a7f3005857076f2618fffe5","tid":1627252,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"而家小朋友被告暴動襲警係荒謬<br />\n係原告變被告<br />\n一定要告返個開槍黑警同政府<br />\n<br />\n1) 冇人知小朋友中槍時企喺邊<br />\n佢驚慌得滯  醒返都可能唔記得當時情況<br />\n因為亦都冇人影到開槍時嘅角度<br />\n小朋友好可能只係喺路邊中流彈<br />\n<br />\n2) 當時黑警附近全部人black bloc<br />\n小朋友做完手術<br />\n冇人知佢本身著乜衫<br />\n<br />\n3) 黑警當時開槍完全不合法<br />\n因為冇生命危險 (仲要開車撞人在先)<br />\n令到路人中槍更加應該要判刑<br />\n政府亦要鉅額賠償畀小朋友<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手推到畀小朋友同佢親友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc5a04f05a5f89e79326bc83974780af6978ec4","tid":1627252,"uid":69280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a6efca85763633ec363ea37bfaa8a3791ec5dee","tid":1627252,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc5a04f05a5f89e79326bc83974780af6978ec4","tid":1627252,"uid":69280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b41f67c199ad73b817e3f88aeefcb2823393ad","tid":1627252,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df3637d7f0ee125149f5db099400ce0880910811","tid":1627252,"uid":268050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721有曬證據搞咁耐先得嗰dd白衣人被告暴動<br />\n而家連片都影唔到14歲少年當時做緊乜就一口咬定告佢暴動？係咪傻撚左啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單野擺撚明係黑警嘅錯啦 dklm"},{"pid":"24d1614581ddc03ea3bc87a1d06b7eda7ca57dd